text:
Toru, would you like to try being in that kind of CM?
If you're interested, I can arrange it next time.

Can you make it?
If you do it, do it with clarity.

Eh... Ah, no, Toru, you're already clear enough
even without appearing in a commercial.

Yeah.
You're not inferior to the girl in that commercial.

Is that so?
If Toru wants to do it, don't hesitate────

But you're capable, right?
With clarity.

I'll do it, so tomorrow too,
Clang.
